msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍທີ່ລົງບັນຊີ ຫຼື ຊຳລະແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense/models/analytic.py:0
#, python-format
msgid "You cannot delete an analytic account that is used in an expense."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບບັນຊີວິເຄາະທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້ໃນຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍໃດໜຶ່ງ."

#. module: hr_expense
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense/models/account_payment.py:0
#, python-format
msgid "You cannot do this modification since the payment is linked to an expense report."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ ເພາະການຊຳລະເງິນນີ້ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບບົດລາຍງານຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍ."

